{"tid":1831161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日九龍城區議會要人！","createTime":"2020-01-20T07:50:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T09:21:08.000Z","uid":142903,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8af09d1175d803838f4f0860802eb1e38a12b99b","tid":1831161,"uid":142903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T07:50:13.000Z","msg":"又可以睇李慧琼潘國華出黎柒啦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/veJ2mji.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FveJ2mji.jpg&h=dc6db740&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>要求交代九龍城區催淚彈及水炮車使用情況及善後工作<br />\n要求警方交代自殺死亡、屍體發現案及失蹤人口情況<br />\n檢討催淚彈對公共衛生的影響<br />\n強烈譴責教育局局長帶頭製造白色恐怖<br />\n動議：譴責香港警察沒有依循警隊條例<br />\n動議：要求立即正面回應五大訴求<br />\n動議：本會要求行政長官林鄭月娥立即問責下台<br />\n動議：建議否決撥款予警隊加薪及警隊工程</strong><br />\n豉油：<a href=\"https://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/kc/doc/2020_2023/tc/dc_meetings_agenda/6DC_1sca_1.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.districtcouncils.gov.hk%2Fkc%2Fdoc%2F2020_2023%2Ftc%2Fdc_meetings_agenda%2F6DC_1sca_1.pdf&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV9wPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=e33b535b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/kc/doc/2020_2023/tc/dc_meetings_agenda/6DC_1sca_1.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"631602ebd02e5890a41f84376b7f32a469593ddf","tid":1831161,"uid":142903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T08:33:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e53f06d2064e4ccf0c1b33dc3e218ac77047dac8","tid":1831161,"uid":231331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T08:59:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"467f996addaf518c9060bba46f66b8402e85738b","tid":1831161,"uid":142903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T09:21:08.000Z","msg":"我推"}]}